{"tid":2165650,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遼寧虎谷峽玻璃棧道發生事故 1死多傷","createTime":"2020-08-20T03:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T03:44:34.000Z","uid":49776,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"41492e5f120890885d18d6622451391ec237afa2","tid":2165650,"uid":49776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"（看中國記者黎小葵綜合報導）19日下午，遼寧省本溪桓仁虎谷峽景區內一處玻璃棧道遊樂設施發生事故，造成1人死亡、多人受傷，但詭異的是，官方迄今未作出具體說明，傷者送往醫院後，情況也不明朗。<br />\n虎穀峽玻璃棧道出事 釀一死多傷<br />\n<br />\n大陸多家媒體20日紛紛報導，從遼寧省本溪市有關部門了解到，8月19日下午，本溪市桓仁滿族自治縣虎穀峽景區內，一處玻璃滑道在營業期間發生事故，造成遊客一人死亡，多人受傷。事故發生時，曾有遊客倒在地上無法起身，是景區工作人員將傷者抬上擔架，目前醫護人員正在救治傷員。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，該景區內發生事故時，當地下著大雨。目前事故原因仍在調查中，傷者情況也不明朗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/qingshanlan/status/1296217827523911681\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fqingshanlan%2Fstatus%2F1296217827523911681&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=c0877c6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fqingshanlan%2Fstatus%2F1296217827523911681&h=dd7c38e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/qingshanlan/status/1296217827523911681</a><br />\n<br />\n大紀元<br />\n遼寧一景區玻璃棧道發生事故，現場多名遊客受傷。8月19日遼寧玻璃棧道發生重大事故，該棧道2027年投資2.1億元建成，不到三年慘變豆腐渣。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fpclBbcft7A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfpclBbcft7A&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=5585c9a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fpclBbcft7A</a>"},{"pid":"4a4fa703a97108d961f43431eb359a3c9aca871a","tid":2165650,"uid":283700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:25:15.000Z","msg":"2027？ 我穿越左？"},{"pid":"49ef56e20800e5e1aabbf4b2e97563858904f9f9","tid":2165650,"uid":37808,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:25:23.000Z","msg":"2027年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62290a1e754fa45b0a513c8ec6da6f77466a8524","tid":2165650,"uid":13176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iUrBEps.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiUrBEps.jpg&h=8f2a66d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會內會將於下週五召開特別會議 將討論健康碼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2164924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2164924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8a83d3b3f041a0326b12260d90e01cf3148ca9d","tid":2165650,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:30:22.000Z","msg":"youtube條片8秒果個仲食緊煙?<br />\n即係冇事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d912ec05cd42eab88e00db7685a0ddb6240da243","tid":2165650,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:34:31.000Z","msg":"有幾撚詭異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3065e6ddf5dfc7476cb923075385f778a4a0ed","tid":2165650,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:34:36.000Z","msg":"2027 + 大妓院 = dont waste time to read"},{"pid":"a142cce5b2e6af795743e676e6e5bb111711746b","tid":2165650,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"df3065e6ddf5dfc7476cb923075385f778a4a0ed","tid":2165650,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:34:36.000Z","msg":"2027 + 大妓院 = dont waste time to read"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200820/XFHRDBUT5ZD5VDQ2R6BDLUO5MI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200820%2FXFHRDBUT5ZD5VDQ2R6BDLUO5MI%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=7efca117\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200820%2FXFHRDBUT5ZD5VDQ2R6BDLUO5MI%2F&h=707540ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200820/XFHRDBUT5ZD5VDQ2R6BDLUO5MI/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔啱嘅睇蘋果囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdd205005ad188a572141d878a1eae1b417303f","tid":2165650,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:41:14.000Z","msg":"睇錯遼寧號"},{"pid":"bec58758c4a81a1c70f92273070152d118f42871","tid":2165650,"uid":49776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a142cce5b2e6af795743e676e6e5bb111711746b","tid":2165650,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"df3065e6ddf5dfc7476cb923075385f778a4a0ed","tid":2165650,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:34:36.000Z","msg":"2027 + 大妓院 = dont waste time to read"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200820/XFHRDBUT5ZD5VDQ2R6BDLUO5MI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200820%2FXFHRDBUT5ZD5VDQ2R6BDLUO5MI%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=7efca117\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200820%2FXFHRDBUT5ZD5VDQ2R6BDLUO5MI%2F&h=707540ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200820/XFHRDBUT5ZD5VDQ2R6BDLUO5MI/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔啱嘅睇蘋果囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:41:45.000Z","msg":"網民批評內媒報道模糊焦點：「（新聞）也不說原因，大家還以為是玻璃棧道上的玻璃碎了呢，我在當地才知道是昨天下雨，路面太滑導致的人員踩踏。」「服了哈，翻了一圈報道沒有一個說清楚到底甚麼事故，還要去評論區才知道是因為突如其來的暴雨導致的踩踏事故，要不看新聞配的視頻都以為玻璃棧道塌⋯⋯現在的新聞媒體就這樣！」「太滑踩踏！踩踏！踩踏！別聽xyz瞎帶節奏！ 玻璃沒事！ 希望人平安。」<br />\n<br />\n原來蘑菇踩蘑菇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a566dec11e05c6ad9190467c18d30955778efb7","tid":2165650,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:44:34.000Z","msg":"條片入面影到條玻璃棧道個入口就咁整斜坡就算<br />\n一濕咪免費滑水梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}